{"title":"Cap1 Prehospital iPad","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/UCI-Medicina Crítica/Cap1 Prehospital iPad.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"Cap 1 - Manejo Prehospitalario\\Ndel Adulto Mayor","guid":"PM5igRSzVNebbNqlkqLltA","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"Epidemiología","guid":"","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"AM ≥65a = 38% de todos los pacientes EMS (EE.UU.)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"3","parent":"1","text":"Uso EMS ~4x mayor que paciente joven","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"4","parent":"1","text":"50% de AM atendidos en SU son admitidos → vs 16% en <65a (UK, 2014-2015)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"5","parent":"1","text":">25% de visitas SU serán de AM para 2030","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"6","parent":"1","text":"Mayor mortalidad, dependencia y institucionalización post-SU","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"7","parent":"0","text":"Cambios\\NFisiológicos\\NClave","guid":"Y_e9XhGn7BYhoJklJwytvA","children":[{"id":"8","parent":"7","text":"Neurológico","guid":"","children":[{"id":"9","parent":"8","text":"↓ flujo cerebral → ↓ perfusión/oxigenación","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"10","parent":"8","text":"↓ conducción nerviosa periférica → ↓ percepción de dolor/injuria","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"11","parent":"8","text":"Alteración termorregulación → riesgo HIPOTERMIA","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"12","parent":"7","text":"Sensorial","guid":"","children":[{"id":"13","parent":"12","text":"↓ percepción del entorno → ↑ riesgo caídas","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"14","parent":"12","text":"↑ riesgo lesiones por presión e inmovilización prolongada","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"15","parent":"7","text":"Musculoesquelético","guid":"","children":[{"id":"16","parent":"15","text":"↓ elasticidad piel y colágeno → desgarro cutáneo + hematoma subcutáneo","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"17","parent":"15","text":"Anticoagulantes agravan pérdida de sangre subcutánea","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"18","parent":"7","text":"Vía aérea","guid":"","children":[{"id":"19","parent":"18","text":"Prótesis dentales → riesgo obstrucción/dificultad instrumentación","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"20","parent":"18","text":"Artrosis cervical → ↓ movilidad cuello → laringoscopía difícil","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"21","parent":"18","text":"Inducción de secuencia rápida → REDUCIR dosis de inductores y relajantes","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"22","parent":"7","text":"Respiratorio","guid":"","children":[{"id":"23","parent":"22","text":"↓ reserva pulmonar → aplicar O2 precozmente","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"24","parent":"22","text":"EPOC: evitar hipercarbia → monitorizar ETCO2","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"25","parent":"7","text":"Cardiovascular/trauma","guid":"","children":[{"id":"26","parent":"25","text":"Respuesta a sangrado/shock DIFERENTE al joven","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"27","parent":"25","text":"AM x5 más probabilidad de morir por trauma similar","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"28","parent":"25","text":"MVC: mortalidad ~2x mayor; ~25% sufren fx costales/flail","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"29","parent":"0","text":"Presentación\\NClínica","guid":"NNbcbgEr4AzjrAi4eH-90Q","children":[{"id":"30","parent":"29","text":"Motivos de consulta\\NEMS frecuentes","guid":"I9Hp9Pv2few-111IycKT7w","children":[{"id":"31","parent":"30","text":"Dolor","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"32","parent":"30","text":"Caídas","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"33","parent":"30","text":"Trastornos de marcha","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"34","parent":"30","text":"Trauma","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"35","parent":"30","text":"Confusión/delirium","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"36","parent":"30","text":"Debilidad neurológica","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"37","parent":"30","text":"Depresión","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"38","parent":"30","text":"Dolor torácico","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"39","parent":"29","text":"PRESENTACIÓN ATÍPICA O INESPECÍFICA\\N→ regla en AM","guid":"WZ0tlMb-_3D1HNBmyCGk9A","children":[{"id":"40","parent":"39","text":"Síntomas reflejan mezcla de patología crónica","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"41","parent":"39","text":"Holistic approach obligatorio → cognición, caídas, red social, maltrato, salud mental","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"42","parent":"29","text":"POLIPATOLOGÍA → no todas las patologías previas son causa del evento actual","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"43","parent":"0","text":"Patologías\\NTIEMPO-CRÍTICAS","guid":"Ean06Kz4mvc-dRxddCPqHg","children":[{"id":"44","parent":"43","text":"ACV → fibrinólisis <3h reduce discapacidad severa","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"45","parent":"43","text":"IAM (STEMI) → PTCA/fibrinólisis <6h; PTCA preferida si disponible","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"46","parent":"43","text":"Trauma múltiple → traslado RÁPIDO a centro de trauma","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"47","parent":"43","text":"Neumonía → antibióticos precoces mejoran recuperación","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"48","parent":"43","text":"Abdomen quirúrgico → mayor incidencia en AM (colecistitis, obstrucción, isquemia mesentérica, ruptura aórtica, apendicitis) → cirugía precoz evita perforación/peritonitis","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"49","parent":"0","text":"Manejo del Trauma\\NPrehospitalario","guid":"dNcdfyUr7lGuIAF7_TykYQ","children":[{"id":"50","parent":"49","text":"Comorbilidades y polifarmacia → consecuencias devastadoras ante traumatismo menor","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"51","parent":"49","text":"Score ASA = predictor independiente de mortalidad traumática","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"52","parent":"49","text":"Vía aérea","guid":"","children":[{"id":"53","parent":"52","text":"Precaución con prótesis dentales","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"54","parent":"52","text":"Restricción cervical por artrosis → laringoscopía difícil","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"55","parent":"52","text":"RSI → reducir dosis (hipercalemia, trastornos neuromusculares)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"56","parent":"49","text":"Ventilación","guid":"","children":[{"id":"57","parent":"56","text":"O2 precoz para evitar hipoxia","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"58","parent":"56","text":"ETCO2 → correlaciona con outcome en trauma e intubados","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"59","parent":"49","text":"Circulación","guid":"","children":[{"id":"60","parent":"59","text":"Cristaloides en trauma → PERJUDICIAL en grandes volúmenes","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"61","parent":"59","text":"HIPOTENSIÓN PERMISIVA → técnica válida en AM (no afecta outcomes quirúrgicos)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"62","parent":"59","text":"Control hemorragia → dispositivos compresión; evitar taping piel a piel","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"63","parent":"49","text":"Inmovilización","guid":"","children":[{"id":"64","parent":"63","text":"↑ riesgo úlceras por presión y decondicionamiento","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"65","parent":"63","text":"Considerar protección de extremidades","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"66","parent":"0","text":"Modelos de\\NAtención","guid":"PCMoEfkHN07rQ7w3H439YA","children":[{"id":"67","parent":"66","text":"1 Personal con formación geriátrica","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"68","parent":"66","text":"2 Integración servicios prehospitalarios y comunitarios","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"69","parent":"66","text":"3 Mejor comunicación SU-hospitalización-ambulatorio","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"70","parent":"66","text":"4 Protocolos validados para paciente frágil","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"71","parent":"66","text":"5 Infraestructura geriátrica específica en SU","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"72","parent":"66","text":"Unidades Geriátricas de Agudos\\N(UGA/ACE)","guid":"nFi4NFd75KBgQLIjywdoQA","children":[{"id":"73","parent":"72","text":"↓ caídas vs cuidado usual","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"74","parent":"72","text":"Asociado a menor declinación funcional","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"75","parent":"66","text":"Hospital\\Nen Casa","guid":"P0emaoKFOcVNuxAPRwwzrw","children":[{"id":"76","parent":"75","text":"Cochrane 2011: ↓ mortalidad a 6m (HR ajustado 0.62 [IC95% 0.45-0.87])","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"77","parent":"75","text":"Meta-análisis Australia 61 estudios: ↓ mortalidad (OR 0.81 [IC95% 0.69-0.95]), ↓ hospitalizaciones (OR 0.75), ↓ costo, ↑ satisfacción","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"78","parent":"75","text":"NNT = 50 para prevenir 1 muerte","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"79","parent":"66","text":"Rol del Servicio\\Nde Ambulancias","guid":"WfjCl5mwXhg8D6IQtq9jvA","children":[{"id":"80","parent":"79","text":"30-50% de llamadas sin traslado a hospital secundario (hear & treat / see & refer / see & treat)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"81","parent":"79","text":"Paramédico entrenado en geriatría: ↓ hospitalizaciones 28d (RR 0.87 [IC95% 0.81-0.94])","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"82","parent":"79","text":"Enfermera despachadora EMS → triage correcto 93.3% AM hacia hospital geriátrico comunitario (evita SU)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"83","parent":"66","text":"Prevención de Caídas\\Nprehospitalaria","guid":"rCeXmh7fJRiP69tNxnpzNg","children":[{"id":"84","parent":"83","text":"Referencia a equipo comunitario de prevención vs cuidado estándar","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"85","parent":"83","text":"↓ tasa caídas (3.45 vs 7.68; RR 0.45 [IC95% 0.35-0.59])","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"86","parent":"83","text":"↑ Barthel y NEADL; ↓ Falls Efficacy Scale","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"87","parent":"66","text":"APS y Atención\\NComunitaria","guid":"zn-Hj4qmIPdrF1wFlDG9WQ","children":[{"id":"88","parent":"87","text":"1% ↓ en respuesta APS → 20% ↑ en demanda de atención secundaria","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"89","parent":"87","text":"5% ↑ acceso a médico → 3.5% ↓ en hospitalizaciones","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"90","parent":"0","text":"Entrenamiento del\\NPersonal EMS","guid":"tnAY4HDDj0Ncmj-SsuGJRA","children":[{"id":"91","parent":"90","text":"Escasa formación geriátrica en currículo EMT (sin secciones dedicadas)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"92","parent":"90","text":"BGS \"Silver Book\" → desafíos únicos: paciente solo, cognitivo, polifarmacia","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"93","parent":"90","text":"Formación específica mejora conocimientos pero outcomes no estudiados robustamente","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"94","parent":"90","text":"AACE UK 2014 → prioridad nacional: evaluación del frágil, ética, comunicación, capacidad","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"95","parent":"0","text":"Perlas\\NClínicas","guid":"Pqc4jO_E6mGHQqFuaqCiUQ","children":[{"id":"96","parent":"95","text":"El AM puede NO percibir su propia lesión → buscar activamente daño oculto","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"97","parent":"95","text":"Trauma \"menor\" puede ser catastrófico → aplicar criterios de traslado a trauma en AM","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"98","parent":"95","text":"RSI: REDUCIR dosis de inductores y relajantes en todo AM","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"99","parent":"95","text":"Cristaloides masivos = DAÑINO en trauma del AM → hipotensión permisiva","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"100","parent":"95","text":"Prótesis dental = riesgo de vía aérea → revisar siempre antes de intubar","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"101","parent":"95","text":"1% caída en APS = 20% de aumento en urgencias → argumento para modelos integrados","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"102","parent":"95","text":"ETCO2 útil en trauma e intubación del AM → monitorizar rutinariamente","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"103","parent":"0","text":"VER\\NTAMBIÉN","guid":"4KIGv9rUUn8Sj2mskJSSQQ","children":[{"id":"104","parent":"103","text":"→ Caídas en Urgencias (Urgencias)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"105","parent":"103","text":"→ Trauma en Adulto Mayor (Urgencias)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"106","parent":"103","text":"→ Fragilidad - CFS (Valoración Geriátrica)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"107","parent":"103","